-- Alvarion of Israel Signs $75 Million Multi-Year Deal With Canada's Barrett
-- B y   C a l e v   B e n - D a v i d
-- 2010-10-07T07:22:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-07/alvarion-of-israel-signs-75-million-multi-year-deal-with-canada-s-barrett.html
Alvarian Ltd. signed a multi-year
agreement valued at least $75 million to supply equipment and
services to Canada’s Barrett Xplore Inc. for that country’s
first 4G Broadbank Wireless Access network, according to a
Business Wire statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Calev Ben-David in Jerusalem at 
